{{!
    @template local_opentechnology/techinfo

    Шаблон отображения технической информации об инсталляции.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * labelfor - id of the form element
    * title - Setting title
    * override - Overridden message
    * warning - Warning message
    * name - Setting name
    * error - Error message
    * element - The Element HTML
    * forceltr - Force this element to be displayed LTR
    * default - Default value

    Example context (json):
    {
        "lctables": [
            {
                "header": "header",
                "table": "<table></table>",
                "alert": "alert"
                
            }
        ]
        "rctables": [
            {
                "header": "header",
                "table": "<table></table>",
                "alert": "alert"
                
            }
        ]
    }
}}
<div class="local_opentechnology_data">
    <div class="techinfo">
        {{#lctables}}
            {{>local_opentechnology/techinfo_table}}
        {{/lctables}}
    </div>
    <div>
        {{#rctables}}
            {{>local_opentechnology/techinfo_table}}
        {{/rctables}}
    </div>
</div>
